<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Aamon</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-22 12:16:35</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I got my faction from apprehensive to kindly considers with the cleric guild doing the smash the undead quest for the Thunder pally guild thingy in qeynos.  You just need mass bone chips(200 or so) which are easily attainable just by shouting for them in the newbie grounds.  It may cost you 10 plat to get those chips away from all the greedy newbies, but it will save a load of time.  Its also a good way to get from level 1 to 5 in about 3 minutes.  But the faction changes are fast.  I have about 150 Bone chips saved up on a couple other characters.  I will do a repost of how long it takes me to get to warmly.  Good luck.<BR>
<BR>
Aamon (Bertoxx)</font></td></tr></table>
